string_part     = string_char | string_escape | string_interp ;
string_char     = /[^"\\{]/ ;
string_escape   = "\\" , /./ ;
string_interp   = "{" , expression , "}" ;
```

---

## 3. 型リテラル

```
literal         = null_lit
                | bool_lit
                | number
                | string
                | array_lit
                | object_lit ;

null_lit        = "値なし" ;
bool_lit        = "真" | "偽" ;

array_lit       = "[" , [ expression , { array_sep , expression } ] , "]" ;
array_sep       = "," | "、" | "，" ;

object_lit      = "{" , [ key_value , { obj_sep , key_value } ] , "}" ;
obj_sep         = "," | "、" | "，" ;
